title: Team Cupcake
description:
All he wanted was to talk about Minifans Across America for 30 minutes... What actually happened was Justin left the show, Alex Bennett used the show and now Kirk Minihane is preparing to travel to Rough n Rowdy to be in Cupcake's corner.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
